race.description: Integra Insurance Mandurah Cup 3 Jan 2026 Handicap
race.comment: STARWALKER (2) has been battling to find some of his good form recently, finishing sixth last time out over 1800m at Ascot. Yet to miss the placings in two runs at this course and distance, and with a nice drop in class, he can take this out. FIOREYES (6) missed the money two starts ago, then was a lot better when fourth over 2000m here a week and a half back. He saves his best for this track and can figure in the top 3 this time. AMAZING CHEAT (3) is getting fitter with each of her 3 runs back from a spell, and ran fourth over 1600m here last month, finishing less than 2 lengths from the winner. She has 3kg less to carry this time, thanks to a claim, and she should be included in all combinations. MODELISTIC (9) has also been battling to find her best form, and finished seventh over 2000m here 10 days ago. Chris Parnham sticks with her, and so do we. BIRD ON A WIRE (4) is one to keep safe after a last start win 2 weeks ago at Ascot over 1800m. Each-way claims again.
